Package: RMetalog
Type: Package
Title: R Implementation of the Metalog Distribution
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Isaac Faber
Maintainer: Isaac Faber <isaacfab@gmail.com>
Description: Implementation of the metalog distribution in R.
    The metalog distribution is a modern, highly flexible, data-driven distribution.
    This package builds metalog distributions from raw data. These distributions are
    useful for exploratory and probabilistic analysis.
Imports:
    lpSolve,
    ggplot2
Suggests:
    devtools
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
